sc-dNCsYx jbRdkh iPZmef\">Spacious brick ranch home on 1.26 acres, offering the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and versatility! Featuring 3 large bedrooms complemented by 3.5 bathrooms ensuring ample space for relaxation and privacy. The huge loft space has a full bathroom, offering limitless potential as a 4th bedroom, guest suite or recreation area. Plus the generous garage spaces are a bonus with a 3 car attached garage and a separate 3 car detached garage providing abundant storage and workshop possibilities.  The screened patio is perfect for enjoying fresh air and scenic views while protected from the elements. Embrace the picturesque vistas of the nearby apple orchard, adding natural beauty and tranquility to your surroundings. Experience the freedom and flexibility with no HOA dues or restrictions, allowing you to personalize and enjoy your property to the fullest. Cost efficient utilities include natural gas, public water and AES for electric and there is a full home generator included. Monrovia Schools.
